text: Max Collins-Magno (born Isabelle Abiera Collins-Magno; August 28, 1992) is an American-Filipino actress and model. She was born in California, but raised in Boracay, Philippines. She hosted Wowowee, at the same time she appeared as Veronica in the afternoon TV series Rosalka. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Filipino actors Category:Models from California Category:Actors from California Category:People from Aklan
